<plot>A prostitute is cheated out of her money by a drug-dealer, in the next scene the dealer seduces a maid, who in turn is hit by the son of her employer, and so on, until an actress engages in a little hanky-panky with the count, who - and this is where the circle joins - in a final scene ends up at the prostitute's apartment. The dramatic design is based on Arthur Schnitzler's theater-play Der Reigen, a chain of amorous liaisons in Viennese society at the turn of the century.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?065849</url></doc>
